title: Faber-Castell Goldfaber Color Pencil Gift Set
description:
A complete color pencil gift set, with vibrant colors and break resistant leads for easy sharpening and long lasting use. Everything necessary for the burgeoning artist to explore their abilities with colored pencils is provided.

  • Dimensions: 9.5 x 7.5 x 1 in.
  • Includes:
  • 17 Goldfaber color pencils
  • 2 Goldfaber sketch pencils 2B & HB
  • 1 black fine Pitt artist pen
  • 1 dust free eraser
  • 1 pencil sharpener
  • 1 sketch pad
